		<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 13.5pt">
		<b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: #0643CC">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #0643CC">康乐家园</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: #0643CC">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #0643CC">网的宗旨是什么？</span></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 13.5pt">
		<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">康乐家园</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">的宗旨是：让病人更方便地享受到佑安医院规范化、高质量</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">家庭医生式</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">的医疗服务。帮助入网病人全面控制肝病危险因素，使病人得到及时的治疗、预防、保健康复指导和健康教育。</span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black">
		</span></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 13.5pt">
		<b><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: #0643CC">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #0643CC">康乐家园</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: #0643CC">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #0643CC">网的目标是什么？</span></b></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 13.5pt">
		<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">、通过</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">康乐家园</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">，广大病友将得到便捷、规范、温馨的诊疗服务、医疗咨询、健康指导和心理支持，控制病情发展、改善治疗结果，提高生活质量。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">康乐家园</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">成为肝病病友与佑安医院连接的桥梁和纽带，成为肝病病人康复的温馨家园。</span></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 13.5pt">
		<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">康乐家园</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">系统的建立将成为佑安医院向病人提供精细化医疗服务，和谐医患关系，解决</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">看病难、看病贵、看好病</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">的有效路径。</span></p>
		<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; line-height: 13.5pt">
		<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">“</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">康乐家园</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; color: black">”</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: black">系统的建立将为佑安医院创建一流肝病中心提供医患沟通交流，临床诊疗和临床研究管理的信息化平台。</span></p>
